#: includes/Admin/Test_Page.php:859
msgid ""
"Buttons use the current wp-admin session with an X-WP-Nonce header. External "
"clients should use WordPress REST authentication such as application "
"passwords."
msgstr ""
"Les boutons utilisent la session wp-admin actuelle avec l’en-tête X-WP-"
"Nonce. Les clients externes doivent utiliser une authentification REST "
"WordPress, comme les mots de passe d’application."

